    %% INJECTION GUARD
    GUARD["рџ›ЎпёЏ  Injection Scanner\nBlocks before any write:\nprompt injection В· role hijack\nexfil curl/wget В· ssh backdoor\ninvisible unicode chars"]:::guard

    %% SNAPSHOT PATTERN
    SNAP["вќ„пёЏ  Frozen Snapshot Pattern\nSystem prompt snapshot captured\nonce at session start.\nMid-session writes в†’ disk only.\nPrompt unchanged в†’ prefix cache\nstays valid all session."]:::note

    %% в”Ђв”Ђ LAYER 2: SQLite Session DB в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
    subgraph L2["рџ—„пёЏ  Layer 2 вЂ” SQLite Session DB   (~/.hermes/state.db)"]
